Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:22.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when I gave up on trying to escape from this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:26.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:41.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't get out of it? {I really can't get out of it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:45.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'll write it for you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:40.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:43.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right getting up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:47.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I feel much better today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:49.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:54.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I had always wanted to star in this director's movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:03:00.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It lasted for a short time, but my dream came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:01.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:03.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I hope yours will come true too, Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:08.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have to be grand, but as long as it comes from your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:11.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A dream that will last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:16.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, Mother... since I've found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:37.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:44.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Am I disturbing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:48.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That was a really nice shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:50.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:51.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:54.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're bad at shooting videos. {shooting} {You're bad at taking videos.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:58.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You took mostly my face, ignoring the shot of the ball. {You only took most of my face, ignoring the shot.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:02.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't really intend to take that one. {Well, I didn't really aim to take that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:07.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Take a video of me again without my permission and I'll use my right hand. {Take a video of me again without my permission and I'll use my right hand.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:11.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I'm not in a sports club. {This is why I'm not in the sports club...} {"a" sports club is probably more accurate - Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, which eleven o'clock is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:31.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So Kei didn't come to wake me up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:41.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Is it okay if I kiss you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:49.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:53.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:01.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, about yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:02.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That was unintentional...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:07.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll write a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:13.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But as of now I can only remember thirteen hours worth of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:16.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It would be impossible for me to do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:20.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right. I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:21.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:22.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try doing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:28.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And also, you are responsible, Renji-kun. {Also, you are responsible, Renji-kun.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:29.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Responsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:37.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because you embraced, confessed to and kissed me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:41.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? That kiss didn't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But you did the other things though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That was inevitable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:48.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Were you just taking advantage of the confusion?{Was it because of the disarray...?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:52.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,did you write that in your diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:54.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:58.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dream that I gave up a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:04.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You made me remember it again, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:08.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try doing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamura-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Shindou Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:38.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:41.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:43.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Will it take a lot of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:49.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, you're going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:53.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you really need to talk, then you can follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:56.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it doesn't involve coming to school. {As long as it doesn't involve coming to school.} {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:01.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, where should we do our activity?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:03.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:11.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confirming the time to have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:16.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I had breakfast at seven today so lunch time should be soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:20.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see. We can go to my house and cook something... {make food}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:23.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe we can just go somewhere to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come too, Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:25.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:27.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It surprised me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:32.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm interested in Renji-kun's homemade food. {I'm interested in Renji-kun's home made food.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:35.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Me cooking food?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:39.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just say you can go home and cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:39.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:40.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:44.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're actually really good at remembering things?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:47.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it's within thirteen hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:50.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my my, welcome. {Oh my my, etc}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:53.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. I'm Shindou Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:56.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being polite. I'm Asou Sumire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:59.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:00.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,His wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:04.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:08.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to believe it myself, but she is my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:11.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:17.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is our neighbor, Kuze-san. {neighbor for US style, I think?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:21.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm the man with the shining smile.{Hello, they say I have bright smile comparable to sun.}{check}{Hello, I'm the man with the shining smile}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:21.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:22.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:28.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:32.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm wondering... what is Chihiro-chan's relationship with Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:37.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Relationship? I think we're just friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:40.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well they say that there is no such thing as just friendship between a man and a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:43.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that's how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:46.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Usually it ends up as a one-sided love from the man. {Usually it ends up as a one-sided love from the man.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:50.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I don't think Renji-kun is someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:51.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,He is just kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:52.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:54.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which things about Renji make him really good.{I wonder which part that make Renji really good.}{check} {I wonder which part of him makes Renji good.} {That sounds weird out of context ._.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:09:00.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Since in my own eyes, I think he's an idiot.{she is just saying it jokingly so this line may sound harsh. other words?}{hmmm, how about Klutz?} {Was apparently originally "Since from my eyes..." etc. etc. - Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:01.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, I don't think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:05.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that sparked the maternal instincts? {Maybe that sparked the maternal instincts?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:13.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But, I was worried because there wasn't much news about girlfriends; Mom is so happy now though. {about girlfriends and etc}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:15.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I just think it's interesting to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:19.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So Chihiro, why did you fall in love with Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:21.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you see that you're bothering Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:26.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, right, Chihiro-chan? {That's not true, right, Chihiro-chan?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:28.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,See that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:35.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So you ended up following me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:37.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was the one who said I wanted to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So hard-working, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:41.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're aiming for a perfect attendance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So what is this all about then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:48.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,T-That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:53.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-senpai is at a really important time in his life right now.{Hirono-senpai is in his really important time right now.}{Hirono-senpai is in a really delicate time right now.} {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:10:00.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,He has bad grades, his attendance is minimally safe, and there is a chance that he'll be held back. {or for a literal translation "His attendance is in danger"} {check} {He has bad grades, his attendance bad, and there is a chance that he will be held back.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:03.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But he can still recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:07.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If he just continues to go to school and study properly, then he can become a third-year student. {If he just continues to go to school and studies properly then he can become a third year student.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:11.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you shouldn't make Hirono-senpai skip any more classes or confuse him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we both wasted our time. {We both wasted our time.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:19.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a matter worth giving up the perfect attendance award to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:23.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would hear something more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:28.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a problem of  it being interesting or not! {It's not a problem of it being interesting or not!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:31.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-ch-... This concerns Hirono-senpai's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:36.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that something that Hirono-kun should be thinking about on his own?{Isn't that something that should be thought by Hirono-kun himself?} {Isn't this something that Hirono-kun should handle himself?} {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:44.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to Hirono-kun himself to decide what he wants to do.{original: It's only up to Hirono-kun himself on deciding what he will do.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:46.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something an outsider should worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Outsider? That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:51.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you saying that you can take responsibility? {Or are you saying you can take responsibility?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:56.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can you guarantee that as long as Hirono-kun goes to school he will have a good future?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:57.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:11:05.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can Hirono-kun be successful as a mangaka by not doing something that he wants and to just study? {Can Hirono-kun be successful as a mangaka by not doing something that he wants to and just study?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:14.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun is an adult. So wouldn't you think that he thought properly about drawing manga, skipping school, or studying? {Hirono-kun is an adult so wouldn't you think he properly thought about drawing manga, skipping school and his studies?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:14.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:20.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But... Onii-chan is still just a student, so he should study for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:24.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is being a mangaka really so easy in that you can just quit or start at any time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:28.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,He worked so hard that he hurt his own wrist. {He worked so hard that he hurt his wrist.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:32.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If all of that effort was wasted, then would you be able to take that responsibility? {If all of that was wasted then could you take the blame?} {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan, just a note for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:39.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're being honest at the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:45.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't realize that, then you will hate yourself someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:50.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you go back now you can still be on time for sixth period. {If you go back now you can still be on time for sixth period.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:58.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:03.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that Renji-kun would be really good at cooking. {I never thought Renji-kun was good at coking.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:05.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's the only thing I'm good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:10.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're writing what you ate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:14.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, since I might be taking in excessive nutrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:17.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Today, lunch is ten points. It has been a while... {should be one sentence but cant find way to include the second sentence.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:18.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ten points?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:21.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, my breakfast was four points.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday's dinner was seven points.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a method of scoring? {how good the food was}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:30.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to record them because it happens so often...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:33.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,and it's difficult to evaluate them so I use an easy scoring system for it. {seems like a run-on sentence but...} {It's hard to record because it happens so often and it's difficult to evalute them so I use an easy scoring sytem for it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:36.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Won't that be scary to those who cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can you cook, Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:44.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I can't cook, but I shouldn't put whatever I cook into my mouth. {eat whatever I cook}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:48.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Our family is not so fond of cooking. {was originally family/clan. - Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:51.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you can't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:57.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:00.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's a collection of ideas for the novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:03.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please read it only after I leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:08.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel comfortable when someone reads something that I wrote in front of me. {I don't feel comfortable when someone reads something I wrote in front of me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:12.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see, then I'll take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:14.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So what is especially difficult for Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:16.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Difficult for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:23.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought that it would be a good idea to know and confirm what Chihiro can't do.{I want to remember what Chihiro can't do and also confirm how you do it.}{say wha-...check please. "what you can do?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:25.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of it as editing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:27.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:32.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For me, the biggest barrier would be having to finish everything in one day.{For me, the greatest barrier would be I have to finish everything in one day.}{For me, the greatest barrier would be to finish everything I have in one day.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:34.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So it is time after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:37.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I forget details and subtle things... {small} {Note to Editor: punctuation mistake, next line is connected to this line}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:43.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,and that changes the stage, story and even character impressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:48.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I always had to redo the novel halfway through because it didn't flow with the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:53.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I've been attempting it thirty-one times in a period of four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty-one times, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:59.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will be the one to challenge that.{Then I will be the one to take that challenge.}{time (memory) barrier}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:03.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do myself. I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:06.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. Is there something else that I need to watch out for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:07.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:07.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:08.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:10.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:12.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me anything that worries you while you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:17.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Err... there was this problem during Math...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:20.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A sheep is tied up on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:26.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is the area of the grass the sheep go around and eat? {Was is the area of the grass the sheep can eat?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:31.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It should be the length of the leash squared, then multiplied by Pi.{It should be as long as the leash on the sheep will allow.}{check}{I got "It is the length of the leash squared multiplied by PI"} {It should be the length of the leash squared, then multiply by PI.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:34.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It is said the sheep eat even the roots. {of plants} {It is said that sheeps even eat the roots of plants.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:40.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The grass will not regrow, so if you clear them it will turn into a desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:47.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard this problem, I pictured the tied up sheep slowly dying. {When I heard the problem, I pictured the tied sheep slowly dieing.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I... This novel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:55.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:56.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? {it's something}{check} {It's an "Iya", which I understand is slang for "iie", which is no... So... - Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:59.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been my mistake. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:01.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please forget what I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:07.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then I'll note that in my diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:09.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So you have a diary too, Renji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:21.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan, you're being honest at the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:24.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't have to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:25.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:41.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{Krookie?} Just some drawing practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to draw manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:46.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Manga, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:49.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You need to make a story for manga so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:53.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A story? Shall I make one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro will?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:55.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:57.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because I like doing those things.{Because I like doing such stuff.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:04.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, I bought the magazine for this month! {magazine originally had a note of "comic" next to it. - Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:05.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's read it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:07.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So the main character will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:18.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Onii-chan, between Shiori or Shimiko, which girl do you like?{Hey Onii-chan, which one do you like? Shiori or Shimiko?} {girl}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:19.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:23.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Show it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:27.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, don't read it yet. It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, show me. {Note to editor: add a line? dame desu~}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:33.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, let's go to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:36.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But today I promised Chihiro to draw manga together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:41.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro said she has something to do today, so... okay? {Chihiro said she has something to do today so...} {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:44.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:46.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:56.99,ef[Default2],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan there, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.66,ef[Default2],,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:19.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:26.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I tried to gain an advantage. {other word- stealing a march on - idiom}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:30.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the right to tell him my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:33.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that an excuse you made for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:38.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You've been running in the same place all along... {You've been running in the same place this whole time} {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:39.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:45.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,while wishing and waiting for someone that will come and take you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:50.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Kei? I need to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:57.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I can't talk over the phone, so can you meet with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:59.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:05.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:07.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You are welcome here any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:09.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:16.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:17.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:21.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met before, Kuze-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:27.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm friends with Himura so I know everything about you, Chihiro. {I heard HImura, check?} {Well I'm friends with (s)Himura so I know everything about you, Chihiro.} {Changing it to Himura to keep consistency. - Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see. As I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:30.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:35.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, shall I teach you a poem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:36.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A poem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:39.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How many mountains and rivers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:41.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,must I cross before I reach that country...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:43.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,where my loneliness will end?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:44.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Today too I shall journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's by Wakayama Bokusui.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:49.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:55.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How big of a mountain or river do you have to cross in order to go to a country without loneliness?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:19:01.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,We know there is no such thing, but let's start a new journey today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:06.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's about sadness, but the poem is pretty cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:08.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I learned this poem from Himura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:13.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,He must have remembered the poem for someone for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:18.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:19.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:21.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Did you enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:22.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:24.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:29.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry for calling you over at this hour. {Ah, sorry about calling at this hour.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:33.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:34.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:38.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:40.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The guy from this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:43.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You know him, right? Tsutsumi Kyousuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,He is my classmate and a Film Club member.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:49.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Make that ex-member now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.09,0:19:51.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,He has something to tell you, Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:52.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:53.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:56.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I want you to go out with me.{Actually, I want you to accompany me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:03.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl is only one in the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:06.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The girl is only one in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:08.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That made her the god of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:12.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She found herself on an island when she began to understand things around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:16.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The island was small, and one could go around it in half a day by foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:21.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Stretching as far as she could see in a 360-degree view at the beach...{She is able see 360 degrees around from the beach.} {She can see 360 degrees around the beach.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:25.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,there was only the sea, the clouds and the horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There was a castle on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:35.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There was a huge amount of preserved foods inside the warehouse of the castle, so she did not have to starve.{There was many kind of food stored in the castle's storehouse so she didn't have to starve.}{start making my own line here} {There were many kinds of foods stored in the castle's storehouse so she didn't starve.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:39.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There was a mountain of books that one could never finish in their lifetime too. {There was a mountain of books that one could never finish in their lifetime too.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:41.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Those things were her world. {That was her world.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:47.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The books were all about humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:53.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"Humans cannot live by themselves." That sentence was everywhere in the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:57.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But the girl was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:59.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She continued to live despite being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:01.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Neither laughing nor crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:05.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She did not need anything that was written to be important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:09.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She was deciding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:11.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She was finishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:18.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"In the history of man, she was the first human to be balanced." {was originally "man/human" - Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:23.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"The statistical balance of a single person...{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:25.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,is identical with one's self."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:30.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"That is why everything she does is correct." {That is why everything she does is correct.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:35.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"But at the same time, everything might be wrong." {but at the same time, everything might be wrong.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:42.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The sheep...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:51.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The area of the circle is the square of the chain's length multiplied by 3.14. {There area of hte cirle is the chain's length multiplied by 3.14.}
